title: Opie & Jim Norton NOV 11 2015 Wed.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton NOV 11 2015 Wed (03:05:32)

On Today's Show:

RICH VOS & BONNIE McFARLANE, TOM SEGURA, IAN EDWARDS.

They talk about an article out today claiming that a big star has HIV, they talk about Presidential debate last night, they check out a video of a car mechanic getting crushed, and Rich Vos & Bonnie McFarlane join them.

Vos & Bonnie argue. Comedian Tom Segura joins them & they talk about things such as their respective podcasts and having kids. They talk about a Yale College professor in trouble for having an opinion about Halloween costumes that differed from the school's advice to be politically correct.

Ian Edwards joins them & they talk about a movie he was in that was shot on iPhones, MMA stuff, and some boxing stuff including a new movie with Rocky in it
